snippet.title: Cut the Rope: Holiday Gift Android GamePlay Trailer (HD) [Game For Kids]
snippet.description:
FOR MORE ANDROID GAMES GAMEPLAY, GO TO:
http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=AndroidGameplay4You
FOLLOW ME ON TWITTER: https://twitter.com/Gameplay4You
ALSO GOOGLE+: https://www.google.com/+AndroidGameplay4You
For the first time and only during the Holiday Season - Cut the Rope: HOLIDAY GIFT is available on Android Devices! Om Nom wants to wish you the happiest of holidays!
Holiday Gift combines outstanding physics, devilishly tricky levels, and bright colorful visuals with a festive winter feel.
Swipe your finger to cut the ropes and feed Om Nom candy. Don't forget to collect stars as you play!
Extras:
Photo Greeting Card: The Holiday Gift game lets you make your very own holiday greeting card! Pose with Om Nom, then share with your family and friends!
In-App Video Player: Check back regularly for the brand new animated episodes of "Om Nom Stories"! Watch Om Nom explore the real world in these fun adventures!
Already a fan?
